msgstr "Prerequisiti"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:31
msgid "Tax Return Periodicity"
msgstr "Periodicità dichiarazione fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:33
msgid ""
"The configuration of the **Tax Return Periodicity** allows Odoo to compute "
"your tax return correctly and also to send you a reminder to never miss a "
"tax return deadline."
msgstr ""
"La configurazione della **Periodicità della dichiarazione fiscale** consente "
"a Odoo di calcolare correttamente la dichiarazione dell'IVA e di inviare un "
"promemoria per non dimenticare le date di scadenza."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:36
msgid ""
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Under the :guilabel:`Tax Return Periodicity`, you can set:"
msgstr ""
"Per farlo, vai su :menuselection:`Contabilità --> Configurazione --> "
"Impostazioni`. Nella sezione :guilabel:`Periodicità dichiarazione fiscale`, "
"puoi configurare:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Periodicity`: define here whether you submit your tax return on a "
"monthly or quarterly basis;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`periodicità`: indica se vuoi inviare la dichiarazione su base "
"mensile o trimestrale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminder`: define when Odoo should remind you to submit your tax "
"return;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`promemoria`: indica quando Odoo dovrebbe ricordarti di inviare la "
"dichiarazione"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Journal`: select the journal in which to record the tax return."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`registro`: scegli il registro nel quale registrare la "
"dichiarazione."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "Configure how often tax returns have to be made in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:49
msgid ""
"This is usually configured during the :doc:`app's initial set up <../"
"get_started>`."
msgstr ""
"Di solito, questi elementi vengono configurati durante :doc:`la "
"configurazione iniziale dell'app <../get_started>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:54
msgid "Tax Grids"
msgstr "Griglie imposta"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:56
msgid ""
"Odoo generates tax reports based on the :guilabel:`Tax Grids` settings that "
"are configured on your taxes. Therefore, it is crucial to make sure that all "
"recorded transactions use the right taxes. You can see the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Grids` by opening the :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab of any invoice and bill."
msgstr ""
"Odoo genera le dichiarazioni in base alle impostazioni delle  "
":guilabel:`Griglie imposte` configurate nel tuo database. Per questo motivo, "
"è importante assicurarsi che tutte le transazioni registrate utilizzino le "
"imposte corrette. Puoi accedere alle :guilabel:`Griglie imposte` aprendo la "
"scheda :guilabel:`Movimenti contabili` di qualsiasi fattura cliente o "
"fornitore.  "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "see which tax grids are used to record transactions in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""
"Vedere quali griglie fiscali sono utilizzate per registrare le transazioni "
"in Odoo Contabilità"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:65
msgid ""
"To configure your tax grids, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> "
"Configuration --> Taxes`, and open the tax you want to modify. There, you "
"can edit your tax settings, along with the tax grids that are used to record "
"invoices or credit notes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "Configure taxes and their tax grids in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:74
msgid ""
"Taxes and reports are usually already pre-configured in Odoo: a :ref:`fiscal "
"localization package <fiscal_localizations/packages>` is installed according "
"to the country you select at the creation of your database."
msgstr ""
"Di solito, le imposte e i resoconti sono preconfigurati in Odoo: i "
":ref:`pacchetti di localizzazione fiscale <fiscal_localizations/packages>` "
"vengono installati a seconda del Paese selezionato al momento della "
"creazione del database."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:81
msgid "Close a tax period"
msgstr "Chiudere un periodo fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:86
msgid "Tax Lock Date"
msgstr "Data chiusura fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:88
msgid ""
"Any new transaction whose accounting date prior to the :guilabel:`Tax Lock "
"Date` has its tax values moved to the next open tax period. This is useful "
"to make sure that no change can be made to a report once its period is "
"closed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:92
msgid ""
"Therefore, we recommend locking your tax date before working on "
"your :guilabel:`Closing Journal Entry`. This way, other users cannot modify "
"or add transactions that would have an impact on the :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, which can help you avoid some tax declaration errors."
msgstr ""
"Di conseguenza, ti consigliamo di bloccare la data di imposta prima di "
"lavorare sulla :guilabel:`registrazione contabile di chiusura`. In questo "
"modo, gli altri utenti non possono modificare o aggiungere transazioni che "
"potrebbero avere un impatto sulla :guilabel:`registrazione contabile di "
"chiusura`, che può aiutarti a evitare alcuni errori nella dichiarazione."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:97
msgid ""
"To check the current :guilabel:`Tax Lock Date`, or to edit it, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Accounting --> Actions: Lock Dates`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "Lock your tax for a specific period in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:109
msgid ""
"Once all the transactions involving taxes have been posted for the period "
"you want to report, open the :guilabel:`Tax Report` by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Report`. Select the "
"period you want to declare using the date filter to have an overview of the "
"tax report. From the report, click :guilabel:`PDF` or :guilabel:`XLSX` to "
"download the desired format of the tax report. To save the report to the "
"Documents app, click the :icon:`fa-caret-down` (:guilabel:`down arrow`) "
"icon, then click :guilabel:`Save`. Select the format to :guilabel:`Export "
"to`, the :guilabel:`Documents Name`, the :guilabel:`Folder` to store it in, "
"and add any :guilabel:`Tags`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:117
msgid ""
"The report includes all the values to report to the tax authorities, along "
"with the amount to be paid or refunded."
msgstr ""
"La dichiarazione include tutti i valori da comunicare alle autorità fiscali "
"insieme all'importo da pagare o ricevere."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:None
msgid "download the PDF with your Tax Report in Odoo Accounting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:124
msgid ""
"If you forgot to lock your tax date before clicking on :guilabel:`Closing "
"Journal Entry`, then Odoo automatically locks your fiscal period on the same "
"date as the accounting date of your entry. This safety mechanism can prevent "
"some fiscal errors, but it is advised to lock your tax date manually before, "
"as described above."
msgstr ""
"Se dimentichi di bloccare la data fiscale prima di cliccare su "
":guilabel:`Registrazione contabile di chiusura`, Odoo blocca automaticamente "
"il periodo fiscale alla stessa data della data contabile della "
"registrazione. Questo meccanismo di sicurezza può prevenire alcuni errori "
"fiscali, ma ti consigliamo di bloccare manualmente la data fiscale prima, "
"come descritto sopra."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:130
msgid ""
"Once the tax report for a period has been generated but not yet posted, "
"additional invoices or bills from that same period can still be posted and "
"included in the closing entry. To do so, click :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Refresh` in the :guilabel:`Proposition of tax closing "
"journal entry`, or click :guilabel:`Closing Entry` again from the tax report."
msgstr ""
"Una volta generato il report fiscale per un periodo ma non ancora "
"registrato, è ancora possibile registrare fatture o bollette aggiuntive "
"dello stesso periodo e includerle nella scrittura di chiusura. Per farlo, "
"fare clic su :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Aggiorna` nella "
":guilabel:`Proposta di scrittura contabile di chiusura fiscale`, oppure fare "
"nuovamente clic su :guilabel:`Scrittura di chiusura` dal report fiscale."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting/tax_returns.rst:134
msgid ""
"After the tax report has been posted for a period, Odoo locks the period and "
"prevents the creation of new journal entries involving VAT. Any corrections "
"to customer invoices or vendor bills must then be recorded in the following "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Dopo che il report fiscale è stato registrato per un periodo, Odoo blocca il "
"periodo e impedisce la creazione di nuove voci di registrazione che "
"coinvolgono l'IVA. Eventuali correzioni alle fatture clienti o alle bollette "
"fornitore devono quindi essere registrate nel periodo successivo."

