#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:3
msgid "Re-invoice expenses"
msgstr "Rifatturare le spese"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:5
msgid ""
"If expenses are tracked on customer projects, they can be automatically "
"charged back to the customer. This is done by :ref:`creating an expense "
"<expenses/reinvoice-create>`, referencing the sales order to which it is "
"added, then :ref:`creating an expense report <expenses/reinvoice-report>`."
msgstr ""
"Se le spese sono tracciate sui progetti dei clienti, possono essere "
"automaticamente riaddebitabili al cliente. Questo viene fatto :ref:`creando "
"una spesa <expenses/reinvoice-create>`, facendo riferimento all'ordine di "
"vendita a cui viene aggiunta, quindi :ref:`creando un report spese <expenses/"
"reinvoice-report>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:10
msgid ""
"Next, managers :ref:`approve the expense report <expenses/reinvoice-"
"approve>`, before the accounting department :ref:`posts the journal entries "
"<expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."
msgstr ""
"Successivamente, i responsabili :ref:`approvano il report spese <expenses/"
"reinvoice-approve>`, prima che il reparto contabilità :ref:`registri le "
"scritture contabili <expenses/reinvoice-approve>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:13
msgid ""
"Finally, once the expense report is posted to a journal, the expenses appear "
"on the specified :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)`. The :abbr:`SO (Sales Order)` is "
"then :ref:`invoiced <expenses/reinvoice>`, thus charging the customer for "
"the expenses."
msgstr ""
"Infine, una volta che il report spese è registrato in un giornale, le spese "
"appaiono sull':abbr:`OdV (Ordine di Vendita)` specificato. L':abbr:`OdV "
"(Ordine di Vendita)` viene quindi :ref:`fatturato <expenses/reinvoice>`, "
"addebitando così al cliente le spese."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/reinvoice_expenses.rst:18
msgid ""
"Approving expenses, posting expenses to accounting, and reinvoicing expenses "
"on :abbr:`SOs (Sales Orders)` are **only** possible for users with the "
"appropriate :doc:`access rights <../../general/users/access_rights>`."
msgstr ""

