"Odoo, seguito da `/payment/xendit/webhook` (ad es. `https://example.odoo.com/"
"payment/xendit/webhook`) nel campo :guilabel:`Fatture pagate` e fai clic sul "
"pulsante :guilabel:`Testa e salva` accanto ad esso."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/xendit.rst:41
msgid ""
":ref:`Navigate to the payment provider Xendit <payment_providers/add_new>` "
