#~ "attiva :guilabel:`Server e-mail personalizzati`, aggiungi "
#~ "un :guilabel:`Dominio alias` e :guilabel:`Salva`."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The email alias is now available in the :guilabel:`Advanced Settings` tab "
#~ "of the journal. Emails sent to this address will be converted "
#~ "automatically into new invoices or bills."
